---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutMeImage from "../assets/about_me.jpg";
---

<div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] backdrop-blur-sm p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-2xl">
  <Image
    src={aboutMeImage}
    width={1200}
    alt="Pablo García Ruiz"
    format="webp"
    class="w-full aspect-video object-cover rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-xl"
  />

  <div class="mt-8">
    <p class="mt-5 text-sm sm:text-base text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
      I'm a Computer Vision Engineer passionate about solving real-world
      problems through software,
      <em>but you probably figured that out by browsing this portfolio</em>.
      What you might not know is that I do consider myself a creative person who genuinely enjoys
      finding solutions to complex challenges. I'm <span class="text-[#ff004f] font-medium">naturally curious</span> and always
      looking for the next thing, whether it's
      experimenting with Computer Vision, AI, developing web applications or
      starting a new side project. As my mum likes to say, I'm
      <strong class="text-[#ff004f]">"de culo inquieto"</strong>, a Spanish expression for
      someone who never sits still and is always looking for the next thing to
      create, explore or learn.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 border-l-2 border-[#ff004f]/60 pl-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-white/60 italic leading-relaxed">
  My biggest weakness? I can't stop picking up new hobbies. Lately that's meant painting, graphic design, experimenting with unusual recipes and tattooing... I'm sure the list will keep growing.
</p>
  </div>
</div>